I think you are using an older version, because my lines around that in AntiRandoms.scar are:

Case Random(6) of 0: SendArrowSilentWait( ((Random(2) * 2) + 1), 1000 + Random(200) ); 1: SendArrowSilentWait( ((Random(2) * 2)), 1000 + Random(200) ); 2: SendArrowSilentWait( ((Random(2) * 2) + 1), 200 + Random(200) ); 3: SendArrowSilentWait( ((Random(2) * 2)), 200 + Random(200) ); 4: SendArrowSilentWait( ((Random(2) * 2) + 1), 20 + Random(20) ); 5: SendArrowSilentWait( ((Random(2) * 2)), 20 + Random(20) ); end; FindNormalRandoms; end; MakeComPass('N'); SendArrowSilentWait( 0, 750 + Random(500) ); end;

Part of the BoredHuman; procedure…

Although mine may be different because I may have put some extra stuff in there. Post the lines around the error line in AntiRandoms.scar
